_This issue has been moved from [a ticket on Developer Community](https://developercommunity.visualstudio.com/t/IDE0027-ignores-line-wrapped-array-retur/11112724)._

---
[severity:It's more difficult to complete my work]
Use expression body for accessors (IDE0027) rule doesnt work correctly. With below configuration in .editorconfig provided example of two properties which are logically and semantically same they will produce different output for IDE0027 only because of line wrapping. First property will trigger IDE0027, second will not. Behavior should be same for both cases.

csharp_style_expression_bodied_properties = false

dotnet_diagnostic.IDE0025.severity = error #Use expression body for properties (Prefer block)
dotnet_diagnostic.IDE0027.severity = error #Use expression body for accessors (when_on_single_line)

```c#
        public PatientDataInfo[] DatasetsToImport1
        {
            // this is triggering IDE0027
            get
            {
                return new PatientDataInfo[] {};
            }
        }

        public PatientDataInfo[] DatasetsToImport2
        {
            // this is not triggering IDE0027 and it should
            get
            {
                return new PatientDataInfo[]
                {
                };
            }
        }
```

